id: pm-s5pe
title: "Windows nightly: secondary POSIX-separator + mocked-path test class (static-quality-gate, docs-skills-gate, bundle-cli, contracts-snapshot, smoke-npx-from-pack)"
description: "After pm-dita eliminated the SyntaxError/shebang class, the remaining windows-latest script-spec failures are a distinct, pre-existing POSIX-separator + mocked-path class. Tracked separately because the safe fix touches release-critical gate scripts and needs its own careful coverage run."
